### ==================== PROGRESS ENDPOINTS ====================

### 1. Get All Tasks - Endpoint yang ingin Anda test
GET http://localhost:3000/api/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Get Active Tasks Only
GET http://localhost:3000/api/progress/active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Get Queue Status
GET http://localhost:3000/api/progress/queue
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Get Specific Task
GET http://localhost:3000/api/progress/task-123
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Get Tasks by Module
GET http://localhost:3000/api/progress/module/rekon-wt-harian
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. Manual Cleanup (Admin)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/progress/cleanup
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "maxAgeHours": 6
}

### ==================== CREATE TEST DATA ====================

### Create Test Task 1
POST http://localhost:3000/api/your-module-endpoint
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "taskId": "test-task-1",
  "action": "process-data"
}

### Create Test Task 2  
POST http://localhost:3000/api/your-module-endpoint
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "taskId": "test-task-2",
  "action": "export-data",
  "module": "rekon-wt-harian"
}

### ==================== SSE STREAM TESTS ====================

### SSE Stream - All Tasks (Global Monitor)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/progress/stream
Accept: text/event-stream
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### SSE Stream - Specific Task
GET http://localhost:3000/api/progress/stream/task/test-task-1
Accept: text/event-stream
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### SSE Stream - Module Specific  
GET http://localhost:3000/api/progress/stream/module/rekon-wt-harian
Accept: text/event-stream
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}